title: Unreasonable - Malia Manuel
description:
Is Malia Manuel UNREASONABLE?

Women’s surfing has come a long way and today’s women are charging harder and going bigger than ever before.
From pin-up stars to performance athletes, the opportunities for women in surfing are endless.

What does it take to perform at the highest level of professional surfing? How should women be represented within the sport?

Let’s hear O’Neill team rider and WSL top 10 surfer Malia Manuel.

Music: "Reute 08" by Sepalot
